## Diagrama de Sequência: Partida Completa

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant P1 as Player 1
    participant P2 as Player 2
    participant FE as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as Spring Boot API
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant MM as Matchmaking
    participant ENG as Chess Engine
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant CH as Change Stream

    Note over P1,CH: Matchmaking
    P1->>API: POST /matchmaking/join
    P2->>API: POST /matchmaking/join
    MM->>MM: Match found (elo range)
    MM->>DB: Insert game document
    MM-->>P1: gameFound (via polling/WS)
    MM-->>P2: gameFound (via polling/WS)
    P1->>WS: connect /ws/game/{id}
    P2->>WS: connect /ws/game/{id}
    WS-->>P1: opponentJoined
    WS-->>P2: opponentJoined

    Note over P1,CH: Gameplay
    P1->>WS: move(from: "e2", to: "e4")
    WS->>ENG: validateMove(state, move)
    ENG-->>WS: valid (true, newState)
    WS->>DB: update game.moves[]
    DB-->>CH: change event
    CH-->>WS: broadcast to room
    WS-->>P1: moveAccepted(newState, timer)
    WS-->>P2: moveAccepted(newState, timer)

    P2->>WS: move(from: "e7", to: "e5")
    WS->>ENG: validateMove
    ENG-->>WS: valid
    WS->>DB: update
    DB-->>CH: change event
    CH-->>WS: broadcast
    WS-->>P1: moveAccepted
    WS-->>P2: moveAccepted

    Note over P1,CH: Checkmate
    P1->>WS: move(from: "d1", to: "h5")
    WS->>ENG: validateMove
    ENG-->>WS: checkmate
    WS->>DB: game.status = "finished", winner = P1
    DB-->>CH: change event
    CH-->>WS: broadcast
    WS-->>P1: gameOver(winner: P1, reason: checkmate)
    WS-->>P2: gameOver(winner: P1, reason: checkmate)

    Note over P1,CH: Rating Update
    API->>API: calculateRatingChange(P1: 1200, P2: 1180)
    API->>DB: update user ratings
```
